statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `anchong_goods_order` where users_id =29

select `order_id`, `order_num`, `sid`, `sname`, `state`, `created_at`, `total_price`, `name`, `phone`, `address`, `freight`, `invoice`, `customer` from `anchong_goods_order` where users_id =29 order by `created_at` desc limit 10 offset 0
